translations.8322706363855640616: {$START_ITALIC_TEXT}{$CLOSE_ITALIC_TEXT}OSM History Stats based on ohsome API
translations.2433277349625755180: Discover how OpenStreetMap data evolves over time.{$LINE_BREAK} Explore how many buildings have been mapped or how the length of cycleways has grown in your region.{$LINE_BREAK} Compare different areas, track mapping activity, and gain insights into how the community’s tagging practices change over time.
translations.7479500500386644606: Assess the quality of OpenStreetMap data.{$LINE_BREAK} Choose from a wide range of predefined topics.{$LINE_BREAK} Check out how complete, accurate and up-to-date OSM is for your region of interest.{$LINE_BREAK} Gain confidence in OSM and find out if relevant features and attributes have been mapped. And finally answer the question: Is OSM data fit for my purpose?
